The probability of obtaining a knotted or unknotted conformation for the structures modeled by Rosetta was calculated according to a Boltzmann distribution. First, the probability of each unknotted (P
unknotted) or knotted (P
knotted) conformation was calculated as:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
