F1/2 was calculated as F
1/2 times ∆x
(F1/2), corrected by the stretching work of the unfolded state (W
s). F
1/2 was determined as the point of intersection of the force dependent lifetimes of the folding/unfolding process and ∆x
(F1/2) by using the L
c of the unknotted and knotted Arc-L1-Arc.

